Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Refund and Returns Policy
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
This is a sample page.

Overview

Our refund and returns policy lasts 30 days. If 30 days have passed since your purchase, we can’t offer you a full refund or exchange.

To be eligible for a return, your item must be unused and in the same condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging.

Several types of goods are exempt from being returned. Perishable goods such as food, flowers, newspapers or magazines cannot be returned. We also do not accept products that are intimate or sanitary goods, hazardous materials, or flammable liquids or gases.

Additional non-returnable items:

  • Gift cards
  • Downloadable software products
  • Some health and personal care items

To complete your return, we require a receipt or proof of purchase.

Please do not send your purchase back to the manufacturer.

There are certain situations where only partial refunds are granted:

  • Book with obvious signs of use
  • CD, DVD, VHS tape, software, video game, cassette tape, or vinyl record that has been opened.
  • Any item not in its original condition, is damaged or missing parts for reasons not due to our error.
  • Any item that is returned more than 30 days after delivery

Refunds

Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.

If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.

Late or missing refunds

If you haven’t received a refund yet, first check your bank account again.

Then contact your credit card company, it may take some time before your refund is officially posted.

Next contact your bank. There is often some processing time before a refund is posted.

If you’ve done all of this and you still have not received your refund yet, please contact us at {email address}.

Sale items

Only regular priced items may be refunded. Sale items cannot be refunded.

Exchanges

We only replace items if they are defective or damaged. If you need to exchange it for the same item, send us an email at {email address} and send your item to: {physical address}.

Gifts

If the item was marked as a gift when purchased and shipped directly to you, you’ll receive a gift credit for the value of your return. Once the returned item is received, a gift certificate will be mailed to you.

If the item wasn’t marked as a gift when purchased, or the gift giver had the order shipped to themselves to give to you later, we will send a refund to the gift giver and they will find out about your return.

Shipping returns

To return your product, you should mail your product to: {physical address}.

You will be responsible for paying for your own shipping costs for returning your item. Shipping costs are non-refundable. If you receive a refund, the cost of return shipping will be deducted from your refund.

Depending on where you live, the time it may take for your exchanged product to reach you may vary.

If you are returning more expensive items, you may consider using a trackable shipping service or purchasing shipping insurance. We don’t guarantee that we will receive your returned item.

Need help?

Contact us at {email} for questions related to refunds and returns.

item.title: Orange Cutting Foam Pad featuring CCS Technology
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
This Collapsed Cell Structure CCS 6.5 inch or 5.5 inch orange light cutting pad is your go-to application pad for light-duty cutting jobs. When used with a quality polish or swirl remover, the firm, dense foam helps remove light to moderate paint imperfections.
The innovative CCS technology releases scratch removal product gradually as you work. The hole in the center of the pad helps you maintain greater control over your polisher and reduces friction and the associated heat that can build between a typical, flat foam pad and the paint surface. And, the beveled edge protects your paint from the swirls and buffer trails caused by accidentally tilting your machine.
This pad works great with any polish, swirl remover or light-duty cutting compound. Here at Turtle Wax, we’ve found it works incredibly well with our new Hybrid Solutions Pro One and Done Compound. This all-in-one compound simplifies your detailing jobs by working as the only cutting compound you’ll ever need for everything from the lightest swirls to the deepest scratches.
Detail your car just like the pros would! Get tips and step-by-step guides on paint correction in our How-To section!

item.title: Mima Xari 4G Complete Stroller with Car Seat Adapters

item.content:encoded:
The only stroller made with leatherette fabric, the Mima Xari 4G stroller is more than a pretty face. With a chic design and advanced features, this highly-customizable stroller strikes the perfect balance of fashion and functionality.
The Mima Xari frame can be used with either a stroller seat or a carrycot/bassinet—and can change between the two in less than 15 seconds. Thanks to Mima's patented design, the carrycot is cleverly zipped into the seat itself. With the use of adapters, the Xari is also compatible with a number of infant car seats. To ensure the most comfortable ride, the Mima Xari features three recline positions and a seat that can face toward you or the world.
Choose from many color combinations for your Mima Xari stroller, which includes the stroller frame, seat box with carry cot zipped inside, and matching seat pad and carry cot textiles. The Xari 4G stroller includes car seat adapters for attaching a Maxi-Cosi, Cybex, Nuna, or Clek infant car seat.

• Three-position adjustable handlebar

• Highly-resistant wheels, with sports shoe technology so they never deflate

The next generation of Nuna’s most popular stroller features a smaller fold, a smoother ride and a new name: the Nuna MIXX Next.
The MIXX Next builds on the MIXX by folding 6.5 inches smaller than its predecessor and standing on its own when folded. It also offers better maneuverability, thanks to improved suspension and redesigned rubber wheels, and has a magnetic buckle that makes it easier to harness your child.
The MIXX Next includes Nuna's unique ring-shaped car seat adapter, which allows parents to attach and detach a Nuna car seat with one hand. The stroller also pairs with the MIXX Series Bassinet, which is approved safe for overnight sleeping. Reverse the seat to face you or face forward, and recline the seat to a flat position that's safe for newborns.
The Nuna PIPA Lite R combines the safety and 5.3-pound weight of the PIPA Lite infant car seat with the greater adjustability of Nuna's new RELX base. Pronounced like "relax," the RELX base offers four recline positions and solves common installation problems, allowing you to customize the fit of your car seat for both your baby and your vehicle.
The PIPA Lite R does not include the Sky Drape magnetic cover and cannot be installed without the base for taxis or travel. See our Nuna PIPA comparison to learn about the differences between Nuna's five infant car seats.

item.title: 2022 Bumbleride Speed Jogging Stroller
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
As Bumbleride's performance jogging stroller, the Bumbleride Speed offers three front wheel settings for walking, jogging and training. Lock the front wheel for long-distance running, keep it swiveling 360 degrees for city walking, or engage a partial lock with a 20-degree swivel for light jogging and all-terrain trails.
New for 2022, an updated brake is easier to use and sandal friendly, while the bumper bar is also easier to attach and remove. One new color option has been added to the Speed, Supernova with Maritime blue color-blocked with Clay and Sea Glass accents.
With its 3-year warranty and range of use from birth to 65 pounds, the Bumbleride Speed is built to last. The stroller is compatible with numerous infant car seat brands to create a travel system and can also be paired with a bassinet (sold separately) that keeps infants cozy.
Plus, the Bumbleride Speed is one of the most eco-friendly strollers on the planet. Bumbleride uses 28 recycled water bottles per stroller to create the 100% recycled polyester fabrics used for most colors, as well as an innovative solution dye process that uses 89% percent less water.
Bumbleride strollers are free of fire retardants, PVC, phthalate and other chemicals. Fabrics are water-resistant, thanks to PFC-free durable water repellant, and plastic components are made from 25% recycled recycled fishing nets.

item.title: Veer Cruiser All-Terrain Wagon with Canopy and Sidewalls
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
The Veer Cruiser combines the functionality of a premium stroller with the classic fun of a wagon: Whether you push it ahead or pull it behind you, the Veer is a versatile companion for all your family adventures.
With its rugged tires and front-wheel suspension, the Veer can tackle any terrain on your next trip to the beach or the woods. Yet despite its sturdiness and passenger weight capacity of 110 pounds, the Veer weighs as much as a typical double stroller, thanks to its lightweight, aircraft-grade aluminum construction. The Veer folds flat and stands when folded for easy storage.
Accessories sold separately add even more function to the Veer: Add car seat adapters to create a travel system, canopies for sun protection, sidewalls for a pop of color, a storage basket large enough to hold a cooler, and more.
The Veer Cruiser comes equipped with two foldable seats with 3-point harnesses, two cup holders and a removable snack/drink tray. This listing includes the Veer Cruiser wagon, along with one canopy and the sidewall kit.
